"      Zarychanski R, Turgeon AF, Fergusson DA, et al, &ldquo;Renal Outcomes and Mortality Following Hydroxyethyl Starch Resuscitation of Critically Ill Patients: Systematic Review and Meta-Analysis of Randomized Trials&rdquo;",
